lead_paragraph: Influential Everton trio Phil Jagielka, John Stones and Gareth Barry are all doubtful for Saturday's FA Cup semi-final against Manchester United at Wembley, while right-back Seamus Coleman will definitely miss the clash, manager Roberto Martinez said.

headline.print_headline: Everton Sweat Over Fitness of Key Trio Ahead of FA Cup Semis
